  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Active epilepsy

          -  Aged 2-15 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Excluded absence

          -  Myoclonic and malignant epilepsy syndromes

          -  Major motor and cognitive impairments

          -  Those currently receiving antiepilepsy drugs.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
